Trade/Device Name(s): Safety Blood Collection Needle with/without Holder
Luer Access Device-holder with Preattached Multiple Sample Adapter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Jiangsu Caina Medical blood collection needles and luer access devices for venous blood specimen collection
Indications for Use Summary: Devices intended for collection of venous blood with vacuum blood collection tubes; safety needle includes shield to reduce accidental needle stick injury; luer device enables connection to blood collection tubes for blood sampling
